sections.text: opinions; terms, defined.For purposes of sections 44-420 to 44-427:(1) Director shall mean the Director of Insurance; and(2) Qualified actuary shall mean an individual who is a member in good standing of the American Academy of Actuaries and who meets all requirements as determined by the director by rule or regulation.SourceLaws 1994, LB 978, ยง 7.
